      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and slice the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Chop the <strong>capers</strong> roughly</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>capers</strong>, <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>shallot</strong>,<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>mayonnaise</strong>, <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>and<strong> </strong>1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>homemade tatare sauce</strong></p>",
